To the hideout, me hearties.
Follow me.

49:45.849 --> 49:48.985
Last one to the hideout
is a stale cracker.

49:51.254 --> 49:53.990
This way to the map room,
mateys. Come on!

49:55.025 --> 49:59.095
Yay-hey! Let's take the mainsail
slide to Bucky's Grotto.

49:59.097 --> 50:01.497
Yo-ho, let's go!

